outputs.output_descr: The project will support the review and establishment of a case management system for the Supreme Court, provide a Code of conduct for judges and magistrates, develop a Judiciary Strategic Plan, a Manual of Operations for Court Administration and exchanges between Seychlles Supreme Court and other jurisdictions.

project_descr: ENHANCING THE RULE OF LAW IN SEYCHELLES THROUGH THE STRENGHTENING OF MONITORING AND OVERSIGHT CAPACITY OF THE JUDICIARY
